messages.speaker: therapist
messages.text: Welcome! I'm Anita Bhargava, strategic financial advisor and co-founder of Bharosa Club. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help create a roadmap for your future success. Today, we'll focus on understanding your lifestyle aspirations and develop a clear picture of what meaningful success looks like for you. This foundation will be crucial for building a strategic plan that aligns with both your values and ambitions. Let's start with the basics - could you please tell me your name and age?
